# Production: public URL of the contact API (POST /contact) if it is on another host.
# Example: https://api.yourdomain.com/contact
#
# Local: leave unset. `npm run dev` (Vite) serves the site; POST /contact is added by
# scripts/vite-plugin-gsm-contact.mjs on the same port. Put SMTP and MAIL_TO in contact-server/.env
#
# VITE_CONTACT_API=https://your-server.example.com/contact
